1
00:00:48,920 --> 00:00:49,600
Dailing.

2
00:00:57,480 --> 00:00:58,010
Dailing.

3
00:00:58,040 --> 00:00:58,400
Sir,

4
00:00:58,400 --> 00:00:58,760
Dailing.

5
00:00:58,760 --> 00:00:59,440
Sir, you can't go.

6
00:00:59,440 --> 00:01:00,170
You can't go.

7
00:01:00,480 --> 00:01:01,080
Dailing.

8
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,210
Sir, calm down, sir.

9
00:01:02,600 --> 00:01:03,040
Sir.

10
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:47,840
Dailing.

11
00:01:48,479 --> 00:01:49,080
Dailing.

12
00:01:52,280 --> 00:01:53,160
Is that you?

13
00:01:56,960 --> 00:01:57,960
You came back,

14
00:02:00,080 --> 00:02:00,960
didn't you?

15
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:03,800
You came for revenge.

16
00:02:08,479 --> 00:02:09,240
Dailing.

17
00:02:15,640 --> 00:02:17,200
You can even kill me,

18
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:22,800
but don't leave me again.

19
00:02:27,360 --> 00:02:29,160
Don't be like five years ago.

20
00:02:32,400 --> 00:02:33,800
I can't live without you.

21
00:02:36,520 --> 00:02:37,160
Dailing.

22
00:02:53,560 --> 00:02:54,200
Dailing.

23
00:03:00,440 --> 00:03:01,240
You're hurt.

24
00:03:03,320 --> 00:03:03,880
I'm fine.

25
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:09,440
I'm sleepy.

26
00:03:12,360 --> 00:03:13,820
I want to sleep for a while.

27
00:04:11,040 --> 00:04:12,080
I'm sorry.

28
00:04:13,600 --> 00:04:15,000
I let you get hurt again.

29
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,320
Dailing.

30
00:04:26,240 --> 00:04:27,040
Chen Angwei.

31
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:29,940
Are my hands really small?

32
00:04:35,440 --> 00:04:36,640
They are quite small.

33
00:04:37,080 --> 00:04:38,560
In that case,

34
00:04:39,080 --> 00:04:40,920
I'll carry things for you,

35
00:04:41,040 --> 00:04:42,370
carry your exam papers,

36
00:04:43,080 --> 00:04:45,560
and fight off all the bad guys.

37
00:04:50,080 --> 00:04:51,120
I can do it myself.

38
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,380
I don't need your protection.

39
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:54,000
No.

40
00:04:54,400 --> 00:04:56,480
I must protect you from now on.

41
00:05:15,200 --> 00:05:17,200
You're back earlier than expected.

42
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:19,540
You planted the bomb, didn't you?

43
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:23,800
You still got hurt. I'll get you some medicine.

44
00:05:24,400 --> 00:05:26,260
Why didn't you discuss it with me?

45
00:05:26,960 --> 00:05:29,200
You wanted to bomb Angwei, and me along with him?

46
00:05:29,200 --> 00:05:30,530
Are you afraid of death?

47
00:05:31,880 --> 00:05:34,140
Since we set foot on this path of revenge,

48
00:05:34,760 --> 00:05:36,490
our lives are no longer our own.

49
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:41,000
I've already died once.

50
00:05:41,960 --> 00:05:43,159
What do I have to fear?

51
00:05:45,200 --> 00:05:47,040
What I fear is that my revenge is unfulfilled.

52
00:05:47,040 --> 00:05:48,770
My death would be meaningless.

53
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,240
I have to live.

54
00:05:51,720 --> 00:05:54,050
I must watch those villains die one by one.

55
00:05:57,240 --> 00:05:59,840
Ou Shaowen has already started to suspect you.

56
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:02,760
I know you.

57
00:06:04,160 --> 00:06:05,760
You are not that reckless.

58
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:10,340
Why did you do that?

59
00:06:10,560 --> 00:06:12,000
Why did you do that?

60
00:06:14,080 --> 00:06:15,340
Because I could see it.

61
00:06:16,600 --> 00:06:19,530
You simply can't bring yourself to kill Chen Angwei.

62
00:06:19,800 --> 00:06:21,130
You've gone soft again,

63
00:06:21,360 --> 00:06:22,090
haven't you?

64
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:25,080
No, I haven't.

65
00:06:25,200 --> 00:06:27,240
Then why have you been questioning me since you walked in

66
00:06:27,240 --> 00:06:29,900
about why I'm in such a hurry to kill Chen Angwei?

67
00:06:30,280 --> 00:06:31,240
I'm telling you,

68
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,170
he is not your weapon at all.

69
00:06:33,440 --> 00:06:36,300
He is just a stumbling block on your path to revenge.

70
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:40,200
If you continue to act so willfully,

71
00:06:41,920 --> 00:06:44,780
I will no longer cooperate with any of your actions.

72
00:06:47,760 --> 00:06:50,290
You think your wings are fully grown now, huh?

73
00:06:52,120 --> 00:06:53,380
Do you think without me

74
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:55,850
you could have lived until now?

75
00:06:57,800 --> 00:06:58,659
Let's find out.

76
00:07:05,440 --> 00:07:07,570
You don't treat me as a sister anymore.

77
00:07:07,920 --> 00:07:08,360
Right?

78
00:07:11,320 --> 00:07:12,480
I never said that.

79
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:21,400
Danpa.

80
00:07:22,440 --> 00:07:23,320
I did this.

81
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:25,400
Are you satisfied?

82
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,360
This necklace

83
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,600
belongs to Mom.

84
00:08:00,560 --> 00:08:02,160
Why is Mom's necklace here?

85
00:08:03,480 --> 00:08:04,760
Did he keep it

86
00:08:05,480 --> 00:08:07,160
to remember Mom,

87
00:08:08,480 --> 00:08:10,680
or is he deliberately testing me again?

88
00:08:14,600 --> 00:08:15,200
Feifei.

89
00:08:20,040 --> 00:08:21,100
What are you doing?

90
00:08:23,920 --> 00:08:24,480
I came

91
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:27,760
to say thank you.

92
00:08:29,400 --> 00:08:30,130
Come with me.

93
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:32,740
Help me dry my hair.

94
00:08:37,400 --> 00:08:39,799
There's no need to say thank you between us.

95
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,320
I know.

96
00:08:49,840 --> 00:08:51,440
You don't trust me right now,

97
00:08:51,520 --> 00:08:52,450
but that's okay.

98
00:08:54,760 --> 00:08:56,360
As long as you stay by my side,

99
00:08:57,920 --> 00:08:58,780
that's enough.

100
00:09:12,280 --> 00:09:13,340
Help me dry my hair.

101
00:09:48,280 --> 00:09:48,810
Dailing.

102
00:09:49,560 --> 00:09:50,120
Dailing.

103
00:10:12,880 --> 00:10:15,040
You've gone soft again, haven't you?

104
00:10:16,160 --> 00:10:17,880
He isn't your weapon at all.

105
00:10:18,160 --> 00:10:20,960
He is just a stumbling block on the path to revenge.

106
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,820
I'll wait for you outside.

107
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:40,800
It's you.

108
00:10:43,040 --> 00:10:43,700
Sister Hua.

109
00:10:45,600 --> 00:10:47,400
I came here today to tell you that

110
00:10:48,400 --> 00:10:49,520
Feifei is Dailing.
